displayName: Great Rock Castle, Innermost Chamber of Sealing

parameters:
Witch Anat of the Great Rock Castle: Hehehe, you've come
back without learning your lesson, huh?

Witch Relm: Alright, your reckless behavior ends here! The
genius of the Magic Academy will take you on seriously.

Witch Anat of the Great Rock Castle: The crystal is merely a
supplementary item... Don't underestimate the magic power of
this outfit itself.

Witch Anat of the Great Rock Castle: Hehehe, how about it?
Anat will show you who the real genius is!

Witch Relm: This is my line! I'll make sure you understand
that I'm the genius!

Witch Relm: Everyone, let's go! I'll show you the pride of a
witch!
Witch Anat of the Great Rock Castle: Ugh... my body...!
Witch Relm: Please calm down! Take a deep breath.

Witch Relm: It's an image of controlling the flow of magic
power!

Witch Anat of the Great Rock Castle: Ugh... impossible...! I
broke the clan's rules... ugh... it's impossible!

Clea: Please calm down. Your father asked me to request that
of you.

Clea: You're a genius, right? If you're a genius, you should
be able to control magic power.

Witch Relm: I'll support you too, so don't give up and try
to control your magic power!

Witch Relm: If there are two geniuses, then nothing is
impossible, right?

Priestess Sophia: This should do...! I think you'll be fine
if you rest slowly.
Priestess Sophia: Please make sure not to overdo it, okay?
Witch Anat of the Great Rock Castle: T-Thank you...
Thief Nora: A-Are you okay, Relm-san...?

Witch Relm: Ngh... O-Oh... I used too much magic power... My
body...

Witch Anat of the Great Rock Castle: Thank you... If you
weren't here, Anat would have...

Witch Relm: You don't have to worry. We can't overlook the
loss of a talented magician.

Witch Relm: Besides, it's like my duty as a great genius to
save you!

Witch Anat of the Great Rock Castle: Haa, that's not true,
right? I think Anat's magical power is overwhelmingly
superior.

Witch Anat of the Great Rock Castle: This time was just an
accident, you know. If you're a great genius, then Anat is a
super genius, right?

Witch Relm: Huh!? What do you think you're doing, getting
all cocky!

Thief Nora: Both of you just recovered from an illness, so I
don't think it's a good idea to fight, you know~?
Witch Relm: Nora-san, whose side are you on!?

Thief Nora: E-Eek!? Please don't look at me with such a
scary face!
Clea: Relm-san seems to be having fun, doesn't she?

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, I wonder if magicians get along well
with each other?

Priestess Sophia: Well then, let's go report to the head of
the family, Leso-san.

Clea: Yes, I'm sure you're also worried about Anat-san's
safety, right?
